Hawthorn coach Alastair Clarkson was filmed lashing out at an Adelaide Power fan after his team's loss to Port Adelaide on Saturday night . 
  Clarkson was approached by the man as he made his way back to his hotel room . 
  Hawthorn CEO Stuart Fox says Clarkson was 'pushed and shoved all the way to the door' The man is thought to be a Port Adelaide fan . 
  Clarkson grabbed the man by the neck and shoved him . 
  The incident took place after the Hawks' narrow loss to the Power . 
 